Measure error/fit metrics for forecasts

Source: R/process_casts.R
measure_cast_level_error.Rd

Summarize the cast-level errors or fits to the observations.
Presently included are root mean square error and coverage.

measure_cast_level_error(cast_tab = NULL, arg_checks = TRUE)

Arguments

cast_tab

A data.frame of a cast's output. See read_cast_tab.
arg_checks

logical value of if the arguments should be checked using standard protocols via check_args. The default (arg_checks = TRUE) ensures that all inputs are formatted correctly and provides directed error messages if not.

Value

data.frame of metrics for each cast for each species.

Examples

  setup_dir()
